task.summary: Fixed issue on server start with 1.12 related to Bukkit.getOnlinePlayers()

Fixed issues with AutoEye breaking on server reload. Added the ability for AutoEye to cancel packets. Added the Invalid Location check which checks to see if the player is trying to move to a block that is not loaded by the world.
Converted all Reflections to a static variable to reduce runtime overhead as recommended by xTrollxDudex.
Fixed several false positives from the issues section.
Fixed Step bypass, fixed error on 1.12 servers, and renamed derp to Invalid Pitch.
Removed Event System to increase runtime performance.
Removed some more residue files left over from deleting the event system.
Fixed Invalid Motion false positives on teleport. Made AutoEye start detecting if a player is gliding with Elytra to fix falses.
Fixed teleport bypass, improved Invalid Location check.
Fixed permissions, and added a better API implementation.
